---
title: Grilled Harissa Beef and Pork Koftas with Herby Couscous and Roasted Pepper Hummus
description: Roasted pepper pesto and hearty hummus are scrumptious in this grilled kofta platter. This meal is great with hot and cold elements, but they're equally delicious serve room temperature.
